		<div id="comment_body_64339677"><p><div class="quote"><p>All true and informative. What no one seems to be pointing out, is that the judgment imposed by the court is an *insane* amount of money.  This is a clear violation of the 8th amendment to your Constitution. Whatever you think of Trump, this is an activist judge exceeding his authority.</p></div><p>Yes it is insane the for years, Donald Trump cheated people of out $355M. Every penny of the money was calculated from what Trump had cheated others with his lies. The judge did not pull figures out of thin air.</p></div>
